args: Shortly before Laxi connected to\nAyaha's consciousness...
I'll take this tough-looking fella here.
And I'll pick this sturdy young guy.
Great! Now let's watch our berserk humans\nbattle to the death. Aaaand...FIGHT!
Yeah, that's it! Tear him apart!
Hey, don't go LOSING, tough guy! ...Tch!\nHe's gonna get shredded at this rate.
Not fair! You used miasma to make him\ngo even more berserk.
Don't go making false accusations like that\nunless you have proof, girlie!
Okay then, time for another match!\nThis time, we'll have the old man\nand his grandkid fight.
Whaat? You're gonna stop playing? Why?
Only ever playing with you is boring.\nI'm just going to play by myself.
Gonna leave, huh? Say, did you know\nthat demons are veeery greedy?
Once I've gotten my hands on a toy,\nI neeever let it go!
So if you won't play with me,\nI'll just play with you!
You're crazy if you think I'm a toy!
I'm going to make YOU my puppet!
That was actually fairly fun, given that\nyou're a human. But I'm tired of it now.
Now let me hear the screams of your\nfinal moments! Let me hear the ugly\nscreams of a loooooser!
You're the one who's gonna be making\nugly screams!
Aya! ...Wait, and a buncha other folks?
What are all of you doing with Aya?
Temporary truce.\n▷We're not your enemy right now.◁
...So you're saying one of the twins\nis engaged in a fight with a demon?

Otoha's thoughts came to us while
we were connected to Ayaha.
▷It was likely an unconsciously emitted
signal of her desire for rescue.◁
So we're gonna leave her to die, right?\nRiiiiight?

I am worried about the damage that could
be caused by the demon's miasma.
Whether we choose to rescue Otoha or no,
we need to go there right away.
▷Yes, but where do we go? Her thoughts\ndidn't get into that much detail.◁
I always know where Oto is. So if you\nwant to beat this demon or whatever it is,\nyou just need to follow me.
It is true your telepathic abilities could\nperceive the location of your other half.\nHowever...

However, there's no way in heck we're
gonna trust you! You're probably just
pretending to help so we let our guards
down or whatever.
We two are one! We might have fought,\nbut Oto is irreplaceable—another me!
I would never just abandon her,\nso let me go find her already!
▷What do we think?◁\nI detect no indicators of lying in\nher biosigns.
As Ayaha also views the demon as an\nenemy, it would be more efficient to\ncooperate and deal with our common foe.
▷All right. We're going to believe you.\nTake us to the demon.◁
Commencing operation.\nWhile Finni goes to collect holy water,\nLaxi and I will quell the berserk villagers.
▷Let's leave Lilith to Ayaha.◁\nAfter we finish quelling the berserk people,\nwe'll go back and support her.
We don't need YOUR support. When the\ntwo of us are together, a demon is nothing.\nIsn't that right, Oto?
Heck yeah, Aya! Two bodies, one heart.\nWe are the wings that soar to freedom!
And no one can stop our flight!
You little trash babies are SORELY\nunderestimating me here!
Ah ha ha! Too bad, you missed!
Where'd all that energy of yours go?\nEh heh heh!
Damn! Their coordinated attack is\nunstoppable! There's no way I can\nhandle that!
...Nah, just kidding.\nHeeey, you guys love candy, right?
Now shatter like candy between my teeth!\nAah ha ha ha ha!
